<section id='Any'>
<title>Any</title>

<command>
<cmdsynopsis>
    <arg choice='plain'>Any</arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>(conditions)</arg>
    <arg choice='plain'>command</arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</command>

<para>Performs
<emphasis remap='I'>command</emphasis>
if any window which satisfies all
<emphasis remap='I'>conditions</emphasis>
exists.  The command is run in the context of the root window.
See the <fvwmref sect="conditionals" opt="conditions" name="Conditions"/> section for a list of conditions.</para>

</section>
